  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they found some kind of relatives that succeed somehow to find some little more decent place for my, my parents to live, take them out of this shelter, common shelter in which all this people is to live.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that we had some kind of little house of one and a half room that was, obviously, inhabited of some very poor people or gypsies of the town there, which my mother somehow succeed to clean it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we used to live only with my father and my mother in this house, so called-- one small, small, small house of one, little more than one room.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously through some connections, relatives, and perhaps my mother giving some of her intimate jewelry there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what the deal was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember that tree we started to live little bit differently.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother already was able to cook.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the, the life there was not much, much different than the, the life of this shelter.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, was not very far.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or the shelter was also very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she remain in connection with number of people that are living there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This is how they-- perhaps my parents were [INAUDIBLE] of what was happening with the life, the destiny of other Jewish people passing through within and disappearing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some of them were Jewish people coming from Greece, from northern Greece, like Thessaloniki, some of them from, perhaps, Athens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Were quite big groups of people in situation, perhaps, worst.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I remember that they were begging for food, some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Obviously, they traveled much longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I don't know if they had food during this travel that sometime were, were going weeks, maybe months.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In transit, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
